　　111 　年　　11　　月　　28　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCDM/111%2c%e5%96%ae%e7%a6%81%e6%b2%92%2c1038%2c20221125%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCDM,111,單禁沒,1038,20221125,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"單禁沒","JNO":"1038","JDATE":"20221125","JTITLE":"聲請宣告沒收違禁物"}